data.description: Charming 3-bedroom, 1-bathroom home in a great location! This spacious home features an open-concept main floor with a large living room and dining room, perfect for entertaining. The kitchen is well-equipped with plenty of counter space and storage. The upstairs features three bedrooms and one full bathroom. The backyard is fully fenced and includes a patio, perfect for enjoying the outdoors. The home also includes a one-car attached garage. This property is located in a quiet neighborhood within walking distance of schools, parks, and shopping. It is also conveniently located near major highways, making it easy to commute to work or school. Don't miss out on this opportunity to own a great home in a great location! Schedule a showing today!
